    "The papers also consistently underscore the significance of validation and generalizability in medical applications.",
    "Acknowledging the importance of validating the proposed models with diverse datasets and across different clinical sites reflects a commitment to ensuring the reliability and applicability of the methods in real-world scenarios.",
